  <name>Cosmic Power Monitor</name>
  <summary>Display real-time battery power draw in watts</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      A lightweight COSMIC applet that shows real-time battery power consumption
      directly in the panel. Monitor your power usage at a glance with live
      wattage readings updated every second.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Real-time power draw display in watts</li>
      <li>Updates every second via D-Bus</li>
      <li>Lightweight and minimal resource usage</li>
      <li>Integrates seamlessly into the COSMIC panel</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
